    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. For the students though, I want to make sure they understand why this is so important. Could you expand on the section about it being a \"crucial check on majoritarian rule\"? I want to emphasize how this doctrine is actually the main thing preventing the majority from voting away the rights of minority groups.",
